snippet.textDisplay:
In 2024,
Another best song, best emotion & my fav song
Thanks to Re Maan team ❤
We all love you Shreya mam
Thanks to God for sending Shreya Ghoshal to us ❤️ 
Re Maan team is many qualitys to called themselves good❤

I am still studying in class nine but, I have a lot of stress in my studies and I don't have time to do anything like that. But Shreya Ghoshal is my feeling in the middle of thousands of busy. I feel good when I see Shreya mam. And since the release of Re Maan song, I am tired.  I listen to this song only when I feel it.
 For me Re Maan is the best emotion ❤❤❤

Again Thanks to Re Maan team❤❤

I love you Shreya mam.

If loving you is wrong, 😅 I don’t want to be Right ❤️🫶

"Re Maan" is Emotion, inspiration for living in ther World ❤
